WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:04.700
The thing nobody tells you about funding is simple.

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:09.800
You raise money to buy time, not to buy growth.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.800
And that is why he walked away from the deal.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:27.000
[laughter]

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:37.200
I completely disagree with that framing of funding.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:46.900
Every founder I know raised money for growth.
